{
  "stem": "15174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, of course, going to the police station at that time in Germany-- this was the end of 1938-- was not something that you liked-- a Jewish woman liked to do.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In any case, when we got there, there was a whole crowd of people, women and children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it turned out that the Germans, the Gestapo had taken all [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jewish men of Polish citizenship, had picked them all up and had shipped them back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my father and one of my uncles was shipped back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The uncle that owned the tailor shop had already left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I guess he made an application for a visa to the United States early, and they had left for the United States, he, his wife, and my two cousins, a month before this all happened.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he-- he was not deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was-- they were already in the States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, here-- here was my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She was 33 at the time, left in Germany without any visible means of support with a young child.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was five.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you can imagine how terrible that was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And at first, she didn't really know what happened to my father, because they just-- the word was out that they had sent them back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I guess a week later she received a letter from my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He had gotten to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and actually, he had gone back to the little town where my grandparents lived, his parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a little town called Czermin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was really-- that was a village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The little town nearby was Mielic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I guess he stayed there for a few days.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
